function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	-- Lacthan follower's actions
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idActor)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActor, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idActor, marker_Lacthan_tether)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_LacthanCallout, idActor)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, actorLacthan, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActor, actorLacthan)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idActor,animsetKneeling)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idActor, "BrothersBond_Advance")
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idActor)

end
